嚟垃圾，冇醫生搞到醫療水平低下<br />\n唔限制汽車數目增長，冇位畀人泊車，公共巴士請唔夠司機，的士又黑<br />\n政府好多嘢不嬲唔理，然後到問題叢生之時想理，又唔夠人惡<br />\n原來連接收電視啲天線咁多年來都係「非法」<br />\n仲有冇其他？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n澳門好多大學專科生都係黎香港既大學讀因為當年港英同澳葡簽左約，容許澳門專科生黎港讀書。問題係好多人讀完都唔會係澳門發展。<br />\n澳門巴士係政府擁有，車費好平當福利一種。但結果就係服務差...司機就更加..."},{"pid":"950c3e080d4a592869f310dd10564ac6b43f9f4c","tid":497590,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"JR驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9384dafce1af9e1a15f9c85a51e1fc0b5489be5b","tid":497590,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾地方俾狗住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}